How to update amsed ams02 geometry  form /linux/exe/gxint.exe
 
Command [10] rz/file 21 ams02.g3 on
 $ROOTSYS/bin/g2rootold ams02.g3

patch ams02.C add at the end


ams02->Draw();
TFile f("ams02.geom","NEW");
ams02->Write();
f.Write();
f.Close();
 
root  ams02.C



to link g2root

ifx/ifort -c g2root.f
ifx/ifort -o g2root g2root.o -g -L/afs/cern.ch/ams/Offline/CERN/2005.icc64.17/lib -lpacklib -lkernlib -lgfortran -static

